6
</pre></td><td class="rouge-code"><pre><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">foo</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">'foo'</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="nb">id</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">foo</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="mi">139746962569456</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">foo</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="s">' bar'</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="nb">id</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">foo</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="mi">139746962569776</span>
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></div></div>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">foo</code> 변수가 연산을 거치니 ID가 변경되었습니다.</p>

<p>파이썬은 문자열 연산을 시행할 때 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">'foo bar'</code>라는 새로운 값을 메모리에 추가한 뒤, 기존의 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">'foo'</code> 값을 메모리에서 삭제하고 메모리 상의 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">'foo bar'</code>를 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">foo</code> 변수에 연결한 것입니다.</p>

<p>즉, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">foo = 'foo'</code>의 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">foo</code>와 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">foo += 'bar'</code>의 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">foo</code>는 본질적으로 다른 객체입니다.</p>

<div class="language-c highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><td class="rouge-gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
